headline: Waters Surges 10% After New Pharma Collaboration Has the Market Priced in Future Growth?
summary: Trying to decide what to do with Waters stock? You're not alone. Whether you’ve already got a stake or are looking for an open lane, recent moves in the share price have sparked plenty of conversation. After a lukewarm year so far, with the stock down 9.1% year to date, Waters just pulled off a strong 10.2% rally over the past month, following a more modest 1.1% gain last week.
